snippet.title: Need for Speed: Hot Pursuit 3D - Electronic Arts, Inc. (Java Game)
snippet.description:

The biggest, brightest Bejeweled ever! Discover all-new ways to play the #1 puzzle game. Find perfect matches with 8 breathtaking game modes that meet all your moods — ease into Classic Bejeweled for cascades of fun, journey through 40 challenging Quest puzzles, charge into the electrifying Lightning for non-stop action, or tailor your experience in Zen for a revolutionary new way to relax. Engage in endless gem-matching fun and earn flashy achievement badges as you soar to dazzling new heights.
